conversations.content: Please save all order invoices from the current month and save them to /user/invoices. After that, calculating the sum of all payments found within /user/invoices.

<function_thought>

I will start by getting the current day to determine the current month.
Then, I will view the order history to find orders placed in the current month.
After that, I will create the directory `/user/invoices` if it doesn't exist.

Then, I will save each invoice as a file in `/user/invoices`.
After saving all invoices, I will list the files in `/user/invoices`.
Finally, I will read each invoice file and extract the payment amount to calculate the sum.
